								-*-text-*-

This directory contains the documentation for the Turtle compiler, the
runtime library and the library modules as well as my diploma thesis.

If you want to build the Texinfo documentation, simply type `make'.
`make dvi' will produce a DVI (TeX output) version of the Turtle
reference manual, which can be converted to PostScript with 
`dvips -o turtle.ps turtle.dvi'.


Files in this directory:
------------------------

Makefile.am     Automake input for Makefile.in generation..
Makefile.in     Autoconf input for Makefile generation.

turtle.texi     Texinfo documentation for the Turtle compiler.
turtle.info,
turtle.info-1,
turtle.info-2,
turtle.info-3,
turtle.info-4   Documentation in GNU info format.

tagging.text    Description of run-time data formats.


Subdirectories:
---------------

da              Contains the Diplomarbeit.


Administrativa:
---------------

ChangeLog          Change list for the `examples' directory.
